            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>Suspension of Specie Payment</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Banks around the country, including Philadelphia, Baltimore, Richmond and
                    Staunton have suspended specie paymnents. The Virginia banks are sound, but they
                    are creditors of the Northern banks that suspended payments, so they felt
                    obligated to do the same. Banks made a wise decision.</summary>
            </div>
